title: UK asylum seekers to be banned from taking taxis to medical appointments
summary: The Home Office is implementing a cost-cutting measure by discontinuing a service, following reports of its annual expenditure of £15.8 million on that service. title: ‘When I saw what I captured I felt a Muybridge-like joy’: Roger Tooth’s best phone picture

title: The Russia-Ukraine peace deal is not a loss. Nor is it a victory | Stephen Wertheim
summary: The conflict resulted in a ambiguous outcome that is neither a definitive loss nor a triumphant win. It embodies significant aspects of both defeat and victory. This complexity highlights the nuanced nature of the situation.
